de.htw.berlin.polysun4diac.forte.datatypes

Class ForteTypeIDs

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.htw.berlin.polysun4diac.forte.datatypes.ForteTypeIDs

  • public final class ForteTypeIDs
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for holding the supported FORTE type IDs that represent the IEC 61499 data types. They are used for the conversion of byte data arriving from FORTE to the data types specified by the type IDs.
    Author:
    Marc Jakobi

    HTW Berlin

    July 2017
